  "text": "Successfully refactored the sprite generator to use JSON configuration files in the assets directory. Moved all hardcoded values (grid size, colors, body shapes, probabilities, positioning, etc.) into separate JSON files. This makes the system much more customizable without code changes. The generator script is now cleaner and focuses on logic rather than configuration. Users can easily modify colors, grid size, probabilities, and other settings by editing JSON files. Fixed a critical variable naming conflict where 'config' was being overwritten in loops.",
  "sections": [
    "Project Notes"
  ],
